{
  "texts": [
    "7A).Manual evaluation of these 281 discrepancies revealed that GPAD identified the correct publication for 141 (49.82% of the conflicts) (Fig. 7B).",
    "For example, Ehrhart et al. 's study identified Wynne Jones et al.",
    "[38] as the association-making study for Fletcher factor (prekallikrein) deficiency (OMIM ID: 612423) and KLKB1 (MIM number: 229000).",
    "Whereas GPAD recognizes Lombardi et al. (2003) [39] for the association.",
    "This could be because of updated information on OMIM, as this record was last updated in 2022, and Ehrhart et al. 's report is based on 2015's information."
  ]
}